src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 你個份量唔算好過份啦"},{"pid":"db209402bef9343fdebb15be5318341209b86b13","tid":182632,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T22:37:46.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57768aec65f8d2953ab03d04bd6d720bb418524","tid":182632,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:05:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9e70c568f20f3339e1833906865bdc5c30c4cbd","tid":182632,"uid":81824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你見住自己身形越嚟越肥，身邊人開始嘲笑你身形，慢慢你就會開始覺得&ldquo;食&ldquo;呢個行為係&ldquo;罪&ldquo;，每食一啖嘢都有罪惡感，但你已經控制唔到自己，於是你會不停食，食完有罪惡感就去扣喉，扣完喉覺得個胃好空，於是又食，食完又扣喉，然後不停loop....<br />\n<br />\n如果你開始有以上徵狀，先算係&ldquo;暴食症&ldquo;，到時就唔好由佢唔理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 你個份量唔算好過份啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔一定只係扣喉嘅，仲包埋其他補償行為<br />\n(如即刻狂做運動，食瀉藥)<br />\n<br />\n暴食個陣係喺咁場合？<br />\n咩心情之下會暴食？"},{"pid":"0f03ee12ac0eda94c532f1584c0e3e6d30a23476","tid":182632,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同ex.分手肥左40lbs<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果時食到唔停</blockquote><br />\n其實失戀好撚怪<br />\n同初戀分手乜都食唔落瘦左廿磅變左80磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家分手會發癲咁暴食"},{"pid":"cd98425c1101c1073b2a494303550cb7f4eddae6","tid":182632,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:41:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩叫麥麥送<br />\n食左6隻雞亦 一個中薯條 一個魚柳飽 一個豬柳強 一個朱古力新地 一杯可樂<br />\n而家仲覺得肚空空咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多野<br />\n幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好平呀 佢有個餐計埋8x咋"},{"pid":"f1a0a67c4f6ed0245e5aaf15099c0eab9c2e683d","tid":182632,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我最高記錄係午餐食咗批一個大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時M記都食兩個半包加半個中薯，半個粟米，一杯半可樂重有兩隻雞翼同三件麥樂雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點睇</blockquote><br />\n其實我平時唔鍾意食m記d包 <br />\n所以今次食完 罪惡感好撚重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ceccdde56a5608fb63dc651aeb598028989873","tid":182632,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主幾重</blockquote><br />\n52kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想減肥西 想減但控制唔到"},{"pid":"6b243d30a304e7cf4e39f235a1755ef3f2cae29d","tid":182632,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:45:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主幾重</blockquote><br />\n52kg肥西 想減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但控制唔到"},{"pid":"f0d6db464af3655702fbaa74a7c56f9e1d3c385a","tid":182632,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自助餐可以食3個鐘唔停，全場無乜人再行出來，和d食物開始被收起後，我都仲可以一round round咁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食d多種類既野仲特別食得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea88eaad7fc1a2ce6a43810f202f288720703619","tid":182632,"uid":49327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主幾重</blockquote><br />\n52kg肥西 想減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla